{"tid":925870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［輸唔撚起］熱狗向奧巴美揚扔蕉皮被捕！！","createTime":"2018-12-03T04:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T05:11:26.000Z","uid":1009,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c9fd9669944f4f47c95d1e46b2af26d2710ac3","tid":925870,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=87682c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】北倫敦打吡是足球壇其中一個氣氛最熾熱的戰碰，周日一役就有熱刺球迷向阿仙奴射手奧巴美揚扔蕉皮，最終被捕。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴美揚（Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang）今場表現相當出色，先於9分鐘射入12碼，再在56分鐘接應中場艾朗藍斯的傳送，燙射破網梅開二度，帶領阿仙奴主場以4:2擊敗死敵熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n球場上鬥得燦爛，觀眾席也非常「精采」。除了有球迷投擲2個煙霧彈之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">更有熱刺粉絲在Auba射12碼時，把蕉皮扔入球場內。<br />\n<br />\n由於向黑人扔香蕉有種族歧視的意味，警方證實已拘捕了7名搞事的球迷，當中包括出「蕉」的那一位。</span>至於英格蘭足總賽後表示會調查事件，正等待球證甸恩的報告，阿仙奴及熱刺或會因未能控制球迷而被罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLwTbQf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLwTbQf.png&h=5a521cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地熱迷點睇波洗唔洗你廠狗過問啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805d16bd962854936af9651629264e0d7670ea29","tid":925870,"uid":106136,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"輸波輸品<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc96cc0b8bf581778950cf514ca157238c5691","tid":925870,"uid":67252,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"熱刺力架仲多過阿狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30cc65b6faeb409ae22b73fda819aa4d396ca20","tid":925870,"uid":23655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"熱左邊嗰2件黑到睇唔到樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo